d-Cambria@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Coheed-and-Cambria@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Coheed-and-Cambria@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Coheed-and-Cambria@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Coheed-and-Cambria@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coheed-and-cambria">Coheed 和 Cambria</a>分享了一首名为“Someone Who Can”的新单曲，并宣布与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taking-back-sunday">“Taking Back Sunday”</a>进行美国联合巡演。了解以下详细信息。</p><p>今天（1 月 14 日）分享的新曲目标志着该乐队即将发行的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coheed-and-cambria-announce-new-album-the-father-of-make-believe-with-intergalactic-single-searching-for-tomorrow-3814423">“The Father Of Make Believe”</a>的最新预览。该专辑定于 3 月 14 日通过 Virgin Music Group 发行，其中包含之前共享的单曲“Blind Side Sonny”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coheed-and-cambria-announce-new-album-the-father-of-make-believe-with-intergalactic-single-searching-for-tomorrow-3814423">“Searching For Tomorrow”</a> 。您可以<a href="https://store.coheedandcambria.com/products/vaxis-act-iii-the-father-of-make-believe-limited-edition-deluxe-box-set" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>预订。</p><p>在最新的专辑《Someone Who Can》中，乐队捕捉到了一种令人振奋的感觉，并回顾了他们所经历的经历如何将他们带到了他们想要的地方。</p><p> “<em>这就是我们/耗尽魔法，失去联系/全有或全无在水下游泳</em>，”主要词曲作者兼主音吉他手克劳迪奥·桑切斯(Claudio Sanchez)在欢快的即兴重复段中唱道，融入了前副歌部分。 “<em>没有时间回头/像箭一样笔直/进入路尽头的光明。</em> ” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Coheed 和 Cambria - “Someone Who Can” [官方视频]" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mld4KuTNg0M?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “当你长大的时候，你会一直试图理解周围正在变化的世界，”主唱在解释这首歌的灵感时说道。 “随着时间的推移，得出这样的结论是令人欣慰的：你永远无法真正把事情弄清楚。”</p><p>看看上面的内容，以及梅森·默瑟 (Mason Mercer) 执导的视频，展示了乐队早期在纽约的生活。</p><p>除了分享“The Father Of Make Believe”的最新预告片外，Coheed 和 Cambria 还宣布了与“Taking Back Sunday”北美联合头条巡演的细节。</p><p>巡演定于今年夏天进行，共有 25 场演出，并得到了 Foxing 的支持。它于 8 月 16 日在密苏里州圣路易斯音乐公园举行演出。从那里开始，演出将持续整个月，并在印第安纳波利斯、芝加哥、明尼阿波利斯、多伦多、底特律、费城等地停留。</p><p>巡演的后半部分将于 9 月举行，以北卡罗来纳州夏洛特 PNC 音乐馆的演出拉开帷幕。其他日期包括纳什维尔、亚特兰大、达拉斯、洛杉矶、西雅图等地的演出。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fcoheed-and-cambria-tickets%2Fartist%2F852827" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处获取门票</a>和更多信息。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEz3pEoutfJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 5